import pegaplot as pp
import pandas as pd
from pegaplot import df2md

datafile = './data/titanic_train.csv'
dft = pd.read_csv(datafile)

cols = dft.columns
labels_kr = ['ID', '', '', '', '', '', \
             ' ', ' ', ' ', '', \
             ' ', '']
labels = dict(zip(cols, labels_kr))
print(labels)
